# Keep GitHub's language stats focused on the actual Python package.
# The executed notebook embeds figure outputs (base64 PNGs), which would
# otherwise make "Jupyter Notebook" dominate the language bar. Python is the
# real codebase; the notebook and the website are documentation.
*.ipynb linguist-documentation
docs/**  linguist-documentation
results/** linguist-documentation
examples/*.jsonl linguist-generated
*.png binary
